0became%20president-elect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E9%20p.m.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20Polls%20close%20in%20Wisconsin%20and%20Arizona.%20We%20may%20not%20know%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F09%2F22%2Fpolitics%2Fvote-counting-delays-election-states%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresults%20in%20Wisconsin%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20state%20election%20official%20told%20CNN%20in%20September%2C%20in%20part%20because%20of%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20it%20takes%20to%20count%20absentee%20ballots%20in%20the%20heavily%20Democratic%20city%20of%20Milwaukee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Pennsylvania%2C%20Arizona's%20vote%20count%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20days%2C%20given%20that%20most%20of%20the%20electorate%20is%20expected%20to%20vote%20by%20mail.%20Initial%20results%20probably%20won't%20be%20available%20until%2010%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E10%20p.m.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Polls%20close%20in%20Nevada%2C%20which%20could%20also%20take%20days%20to%20count%2C%20given%20that%20most%20of%20the%20state%20is%20expected%20to%20vote%20by%20mail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227329bb1b-3a45-4204-887d-e708e935be38%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20read%20the%20Electoral%20College%20math%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20uses%20the%20Electoral%20College%20to%20elect%20a%20president.%20Each%20state%20gets%20a%20set%20number%20of%20votes%20that%20correlates%20with%20its%20population%20%E2%80%94%20if%20a%20state%20has%20two%20US%20senators%20and%20three%20House%20members%2C%20it%20has%20five%20electoral%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20winner%20must%20get%20at%20least%20270%20electoral%20votes%20%E2%80%94%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20538%20total.%20In%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20states%2C%20either%20Harris%20or%20Trump%20is%20widely%20expected%20to%20win%2C%20leaving%20the%20campaigns%20to%20fight%20over%20the%2093%20electoral%20votes%20up%20for%20grabs%20in%20the%20seven%20battleground%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Harris%20wins%20Georgia%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20and%20Michigan%20on%20Tuesday%20night%20or%20early%20Wednesday%2C%20she%20will%20have%20a%20projected%20273%20electoral%20votes%20%E2%80%94%20enough%20to%20make%20her%20the%20winner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Trump%20sweeps%20those%20states%2C%20he'll%20have%20a%20projected%20266%20electoral%20votes%20%E2%80%94%20not%20enough%20to%20be%20declared%20the%20winner%20but%20it%20would%20him%20in%20a%20very%20strong%20position%20to%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarris'%20easiest%20path%20to%20victory%20would%20be%20to%20win%20the%20traditional%20%26quot%3Bblue%20wall%26quot%3B%20states%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20Michigan%2C%20and%20Wisconsin%20%E2%80%94%20a%20result%20that%20should%20put%20her%20at%20270%20electoral%20votes.%20She%20has%20generally%20polled%20better%20in%20these%20states%20than%20the%20Sun%20Belt%20states%20of%20Arizona%2C%20Nevada%2C%20Georgia%2C%20and%20North%20Carolina.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Trump%2C%20one%20path%20to%20victory%20would%20involve%20holding%20on%20to%20all%20or%20most%20of%20the%20Sun%20Belt%20states%20while%20also%20winning%20Pennsylvania%2C%20Michigan%2C%20or%20Wisconsin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felection-results-trump-harris-presidential-election-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730849590000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felection-results-trump-harris-presidential-election-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Here's%20what%20to%20watch%20as%20polls%20begin%20to%20close%20in%20certain%20states.%20It%20could%20take%20days%20to%20know%20whether%20Donald%20Trump%20or%20Kamala%20Harris%20will%20win.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bmetzger%40insider.com%20(Bryan%20Metzger)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anne%20Hathaway%20Sings%20Updated