are%20killing%20Amazon's%20unique%20culture%2C%20he%20said%20during%20the%20meeting%2C%20a%20recording%20of%20which%20was%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20need%20for%20this%20change%20only%20became%20more%20pronounced%20after%20Amazon%20went%20on%20a%20massive%20hiring%20spree%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20That%20created%20%26quot%3Bmore%20layers%26quot%3B%20that%20%26quot%3Bstretched%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20and%20led%20to%20a%20slower%20decision-making%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20goal%20again%20is%20to%20allow%20us%20to%20have%20higher%20ownership%20and%20to%20move%20more%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20Jassy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJassy's%20comments%20were%20part%20of%20a%20companywide%20all-hands%20meeting%20where%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-ceo-says-rto-mandate-not-backdoor-layoff-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaddressed%20a%20number%20of%20employee%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20the%20rationale%20behind%20a%20strict%20new%20return-to-office%20mandate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20announced%20in%20September%20that%20it%20plans%20to%20increase%20the%20ratio%20of%20individual%20workers%20to%20managers%20by%2015%25%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025's%20first%20quarter.%20An%20internal%20document%20showed%20that%20the%20change%20could%20result%20in%20role%20eliminations%20as%20the%20company%20identifies%20redundant%20positions%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-fewer-managers-leaked-document-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBI%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeter%20DeSantis%2C%20AWS's%20SVP%20of%20utility%20computing%2C%20also%20spoke%20during%20the%20Tuesday%20all-hands%20meeting%20to%20stress%20the%20need%20to%20move%20faster.%20He%20said%20the%20company%20created%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa