20said%20the%20government%20employed%20deficit-financed%20spending%20and%20tax%20relief%20during%20past%20crises%20in%202008%20and%20during%20the%209%2F11%20terrorist%20attacks%20of%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20those%20were%20correct%20decisions%2C%20but%20the%20government%20has%20kept%20up%20that%20level%20of%20spending%20since%2C%20driving%20up%20the%20debt%20and%20creating%20a%20risk%20to%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20the%20resulting%20overhang%20of%20federal%20debt%20could%20itself%20be%20the%20cause%20of%20a%20future%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20Bair%20wrote%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barrons.com%2Farticles%2Fnational-debt-financial-crisis-harris-trump-investors-8608ce19%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eop-ed%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20more%2C%20Bair%20said%20both%20presidential%20candidates%20lack%20plans%20to%20fix%20the%20debt%2C%20and%20their%20proposals%20will%20likely%20continue%20to%20drive%20government%20borrowing%20to%20sustainable%20levels.%20That%20raises%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20scenario%20in%20which%20global%20investors%20lose%20faith%20in%20the%20country's%20ability%20to%20pay%20its%20debt%2C%20eroding%20confidence%20in%20the%20hugely%20important%20US%20Treasury%20market.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20could%20demand%20higher%20premiums%2C%20driving%20up%20the%20government's%20interest%20payment%2C%20which%20could%20forced%20tax%20hikes%2C%20spending%20cuts%2C%20and%20Treasury%20losses%2C%20Bair%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20factors%20would%20cause%20widespread%20economic%20distress%2C%20she%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20parties%20have%20decided%20that%20deficits%20don't%20matter%20anymore%2C%20which%20is%20pretty%20distressing%20because%20they%20do.%20At%20some%20point%20we're%20going%20to%20reach%20the%20inflection%20point%2C%20and%20they're%20going%20to%20matter%20a%20lot%20to%20investors%20who%20are%20going%20to%20question%20if%20they%20want%20to