%20and%20Ms%20Harris%2047.%20In%20a%20first%20since%20October%2017%2C%20however%2C%20Ms%20Harris%20became%20the%20favourite%20on%20election%20day%2C%20leading%20Mr%20Trump%20in%20simulations%2050%20to%2049.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Economist's%20final%20forecast%20said%20Ms%20Harris%20has%20a%2056%25%20chance%20of%20winning%2C%20but%20noted%20that%20the%20lead%20is%20narrow%20and%20Mr%20Trump%20could%20also%20win.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolymarket%2C%20a%20betting%20platform%2C%20said%20former%20president%20Trump%20has%20a%2062.3%25%20chance%20of%20winning%20against%20Vice%20President%20Harris'%2037.9%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Allan%20Lichtman%2C%20known%20for%20his%2013%20'Keys%20to%20the%20White%20House'%20system%2C%20predicted%20Ms%20Harris%20will%20be%20the%20first%20woman%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsign%20them%20(opinion%20polls)%20to%20the%20flames.%20Yes%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20have%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20a%20new%20path-breaking%20president%2C%20the%20first%20woman%20president%20and%20the%20first%20president%20of%20mixed%20African%20and%20Asian%20descent.%20It%20is%20foreshadowing%20where%20America%20is%20going.%20We%20are%20rapidly%20becoming%20a%20majority-minority%20country%20old%20white%20guys%20like%20me%2C%20we%20are%20on%20the%20decline%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Lichtman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'If%20It%20Is%20Fair%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20candidates%20also%20spoke%20to%20the%20media%20on%20election%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20got%20to%20get%20it%20done.%20Today%20is%20voting%20day%2C%20and%20people%20need%20to%20get%20out%20and%20be%20active%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Harris%20told%20Atlanta%20station%20WVEE-FM%2C%20describing%20Mr%20Trump%20as%20%26quot%3Bfull%20of%20vengeance.%20He's%20full%20of%20grievance.%20It's%20all%20about%20himself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20preside