alUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fnagpur%2Fwomen-farm-hands-abandon-cotton-harvest-amid-doles-in-vidarbha%2Farticleshow%2F114991914.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netanyahu%20Fires%20Defence%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20Amid%20Middle%20East%20Conflict%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20fired%20defence%20minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20Tuesday%20following%20public%20differences%20over%20the%20ongoing%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20replacing%20him%20with%20former%20top%20diplomat%20Israel%20Katz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20surprise%20move%20to%20sack%20Gallant%20--%20who%20has%20been%20hawkish%20on%20Israel's%20war%20with%20Hezbollah%20but%20has%20also%20recently%20urged%20a%20ceasefire%20and%20hostage%20release%20deal%20in%20Gaza%20--%20comes%20as%20elections%20are%20held%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Israel's%20top%20military%20backer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20and%20Gallant%20have%20frequently%20clashed%20over%20Israel's%20retaliatory%20military%20offensive%20against%20Hamas%20following%20the%20Palestinian%20militant%20group's%20deadly%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20past%20few%20months...%20trust%20has%20eroded.%20In%20light%20of%20this%2C%20I%20decided%20today%20to%20end%20the%20term%20of%20the%20defence%20minister%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20Netanyahu's%20office%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20had%20appointed%20Katz%20to%20take%20his%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGideon%20Saar%20was%20in%20turn%20appointed%20to%20replace%20Katz%20as%20foreign%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20sacking%2C%20Gallant%20said%20Israel's%20security%20would%20remain%20his%20life's%20%26quot%3Bmission%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas's%20October%207%20attack%20on%20Israel%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%201%2C206%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20accordi