mala%20Harris%20or%20Donald%20Trump%20-%20is%20nearly%20over.%20Americans%20have%20decided%20who%20their%20next%20President%20will%20be.%20After%20a%20months-long%2C%20bitterly-contested%20election%20campaign%2C%20dozens%20of%20millions%20of%20citizens%20across%20the%20United%20States%20voted%20today.%20The%20counting%20of%20votes%20happens%20immediately%20after%20voting%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20began%20across%20the%20country%20at%206%20am%20local%20time%20in%20each%20time%20zone%20and%20will%20end%20at%208%20pm%20local%20time.%20The%20US%20has%20six%20time%20zones%2C%20of%20which%20four%20are%20on%20the%20US%20mainland%20while%20two%20are%20in%20US%20territories%20across%20the%20globe.%20The%20four%20main%20time%20zones%20are%20Eastern%2C%20Central%2C%20Mountain%2C%20and%20Pacific%20Standard%20Time%2C%20while%20the%20two%20other%20time%20zones%20include%20Alaska%20Standard%20Time%20and%20Hawaii-Aleutian%20Standard%20Time%2C%20which%20are%20observed%20only%20by%20Alaska%20and%20Hawaii%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Presidential%20election%20is%20closely%20watched%20around%20the%20world%20as%20US's%20policies%20have%20for%20long%20had%20a%20big%20impact%20on%20other%20countries.%20The%202024%20US%20presidential%20election%20has%20been%20extraordinary%20in%20terms%20of%20political%20discourse%20reaching%20new%20lows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20election%20campaign%20that%20lasted%20several%20months%2C%20America%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20planet%20witnessed%20an%20ugly%20and%20divisive%20contest%20-%20that%20saw%20personal%20attacks%2C%20derogatory%20language%2C%20racist%20slurs%2C%20inflammatory%20rhetoric%20and%20even%20assassination%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHO%20HAS%20THE%20EDGE%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20opinion%20polls%20suggest%20that%20Kamala%20Harris%20has%20a%20razor%20thin%20lead%20over%20Donald%20Trump%20-%201%20percentage%20point.%20However%2C%20if%20the%20electorate%20is%20seen%20in%20terms%20of%20gender%2C%20as%20per%20the%20latest%20Reuters%2FIpsos%20polls%2C%20Kamala%20Harris%20has%20a%2012%20percentage%20point%20lead%20over%20Trump%20among%20women%2C%20while%20Trump%20has%20a%207%20percentage%20point%20lead%20over%20Harris%20among%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20backing%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20her%20promise%20to%20protect%20abortion%20rights%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20compelling%20reasons%20to%20vote%20for%20her.%20The%20perception%20that%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20made%20racist%20and%20offensive%20remarks%2C%20also%20played%20a%20part%20in%20those%20voting%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20backing%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20a%20strict%20immigration%20system%20was%20one%20of%20the%20topmost%20reasons%20for%20supporting%20him.%20High%20inflation%20and%20concerns%20about%20the%20economy%20during%20the%20Biden%20term%20in%20which%20Kamala%20Harris%20was%20the%20Vice%20President%20were%20among%20the%20reasons%20to%20vote%20against%20the%20Democrat%20nominee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20has%20been%20very%20close%20and%20both%20candidates%20have%20been%20neck%20and%20neck%20in%20the%20race.%20While%20Harris%20might%20have%20a%201%20percentage%20point%20lead%20over%20Trump%2C%20there%20is%20uncertainty%20of%20the%20final%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHISTORY%20IN%20THE%20MAKING%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20who%20wins%2C%20Harris%20or%20Trump%2C%20history%20will%20be%20made%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%2060-year-old%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20the%20first%20woman%20Vice%20President%20in%20US%20history%2C%20wins%2C%20she%20will%20become%20the%20first%20woman%2C%20first%20Black%20woman%2C%20first%20Indian-American%2C%20and%20first%20South%20Asian%20American%20to%20win%20the%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20if%2078-year-old%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20the%20only%20US%20President%20to%20be%20impeached%20twice%20and%20the%20first%20to%20be%20criminally%20convicted%2C%20wins%2C%20he%20would%20become%20the%20first%20US%20President%20in%20more%20than%20a%20century%20to%20win%20non-consecutive%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUNDERSTANDING%20THE%20ELECTION%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20follows%20the%20electoral%20college%20voting%20system.%20There%20are%20a%20total%20of%20538%20electoral%20college%20votes%3B%20435%20House%20of%20Representatives%2C%20100%20Senate%20seats%20and%203%20seats%20from%20Washington%20DC.%20A%20candidate%20needs%20a%20minimum%20of%20270%20votes%20to%20become%20the%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20state%20has%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20electoral%20votes.%20California%20has%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20seats%20with%2054%2C%20followed%20by%20Texas%20(40)%20and%20Florida%20(30).%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20states%20like%20North%20Dakota%2C%20South%20Dakota%2C%20Delaware%2C%20and%20Vermont%20have%20a%20minimum%20number%20of%203%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20total%2050%20states%20in%20USA%2C%20there%20are%207%20which%20are%20considered%20battle%20ground%20states%20or%20swing%20states.%20These%20are%20crucial%20for%20both%20candidates%20as%20these%20seven%20states%20alone%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20decide%20on%20who%20will%20be%20the%20next%20President.%20These%20states%20are%20-%20Nevada%20(6%20seats)%2C%20Arizona%20(11%20seats)%2C%20North%20Carolina%20(16%20seats)%2C%20Georgia%20(16%20seats)%2C%20Wisconsin%20(10%20seats)%2C%20Michigan%20(15%20seats)%2C%20and%20Pennsylvania%20(19%20seats).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2080%20million%20Americans%20had%20already%20voted%20before%20the%20main%20election%20day%20(Nov%205)%2C%20either%20via%20mail%20or%20in%20person%2C%20and%20lines%20at%20several%20polling%20stations%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%20were%20short%20and%20orderly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EControl%20of%20both%20chambers%20of%20Congress%20is%20also%20up%20for%20grabs.%20Republicans%20have%20an%20easier%20path%20in%20the%20U.S.%20Senate%2C%20where%20Democrats%20are%20defending%20several%20seats%20in%20Republican-leaning%20states%2C%20while%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives%20looks%20like%20a%20toss-up.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730830380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fuk9sorag_kamala-harris-donald-trump-reuters_625x300_05_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkamala-harris-vs-donald-trump-america-elects-47th-us-president-election-result-today-6952139%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20wait%20to%20know%20who%20will%20win%20-%20Kamala%20Harris%20or%20Donald%20Trump%20-%20is%20nearly%20over.%20Americans%20have%20decided%20who%20their%20next%20President%20will%20be.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meenakshi%20on%20Big%20B's%20reaction%20to%20her%20young%20energy%20on%20set%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730830003000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114990288%2Cimgsize-28280.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmeenakshi-seshadri-shares-amitabh-bachchans-hilarious-take-on-her-young-energy-on-shahenshah-set-these-newcomers-are-lost-%2Farticleshow%2F114990288.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F114990288.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMeenakshi%20Seshadri%2C%20reflecting%20on%20her%20early%20Bollywood%20days%2C%20recalled%20a%20humorous%20comment%20made%20by%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20during%20the%20filming%20of%20'Shahenshah'.%20Bachchan%2C%20amused%20by%20her%20youthful%20exuberance%2C%20remarked%20on%20how%20new%20actors%20often%20seem%20oblivious%20to%20their%20surroundings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22en