20region%2C%20was%20done%20in%20partnership%20with%20Flare%20Aviation%20Consulting%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Three-Time%20Winner%20Amin%20Patel%2C%20Shaina%20NC%20Fight%20For%20Mumbadevi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMumba%20Devi%20is%20the%20presiding%20deity%20of%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20country's%20financial%20capital%2C%20and%20the%20constituency%20named%20after%20her%20is%20set%20for%20an%20epic%20battle%20this%20time.%20The%20three-time%20MLA%20from%20the%20seat%20is%20Congress's%20Amin%20Patel%20and%20his%20challenger%20from%20the%20%C2%A0ruling%20alliance%20is%20Shaina%20NC%2C%20who%20switched%20from%20the%20BJP%20to%20Shiv%20Sena%20after%20getting%20a%20ticket%20from%20this%20constituency%20ahead%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsearch%3Fsearchtext%3DMaharashtra-assembly-elections.%5C%22%3EMaharashtra%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20equation%20in%20the%20constituency%20had%20changed%20in%202009%2C%20when%20Congress's%20Amin%20Patel%20won%20this%20seat%20and%20put%20brakes%20on%20the%20BJP's%20long-term%20hold.%20Till%20now%2C%20Amin%20Patel%20has%20maintained%20his%20influence%20on%20this%20seat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20small%2C%20the%20constituency%20reflects%20the%20cosmopolitan%20nature%20of%20the%20city.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20area%20was%20settled%20a%20long%20time%20ago%20and%20has%20not%20been%20redeveloped.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20little%20has%20been%20done%20in%20terms%20of%20infrastructure%20---%20dilapidated%20buildings%2C%20narrow%20lanes%2C%20traffic%20and%20filth%20form%20part%20of%20Mumbadevi's%20daily%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20constituency%20is%20Muslim-dominated%2C%20with%20the%20community%20comprising%2055%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20electorate.%20NDTV%20found%20that%20while%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government's%20Ladli%20Behen%20scheme%20has%20resonated%20among%20the%20community%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20guarantee%20of%20votes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20constituency's%20three-time%20Congress%20MLA%20Amin%20Patel%20is%20confident%20of%20a%20fourth%20straight%20win.%20But%20he%20said%20it%20would%20based%20on%20his%20work%20on%20local%20issues%20and%20religion%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20confident.%20We%20are%20doing%20cluster%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaina%20NC%20is%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20voters%20with%20her%20government's%20schemes.%20%26quot%3BVoters%20will%20shift%20towards%20us.%20They%20will%20vote%20on%20the%20work%20of%20Mahayuti%20over%20the%20last%20two-and-a-half%20years.%20Women%20are%20happy.%20Ladli%20Behan%20Yojana%20is%20a%20hit%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20alliance%20considers%20the%20Ladli%20Behan%20Yojana%20a%20game%20changer.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhen%20NDTV%20reached%20among%20the%20voters%20--%20especially%20women%20voters%2C%20of%20Mumbadevi's%20Kamathipura%20and%20Dongri%20areas%2C%20the%20scheme%20was%20praised.%20But%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20say%20how%20much%20it%20will%20translate%20into%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20get%20the%20benefit%20but%20other%20women%20of%20the%20house%20got%20it.%20Mahayuti%20did%20good%20work.%20But%20Amin%20Patel%20is%20one%20of%20us.%20He%20comes%20to%20meet%20us.%20He%20is%20a%20local%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20of%20the%20voters.%20Others%20feigned%20indecision%2C%20saying%20it%20is%20too%20early%20to%20make%20a%20call.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20local%20BJP%20leader%20and%20former%20cabinet%20minister%20Raj%20Purohit%20said%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20MP%20Arvind%20Sawant's%20derogatory%20comment%20about%20Shaina%20NC%20will%20backfire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20angry.%20You%20wait%20and%20watch%2C%20they%20will%20teach%20them%20(the%20Congress%20candidate)%20a%20lesson.%20Shaina%20has%20been%20doing%20social%20work%20here.%20She%20is%20not%20new.%20The%20BJP%20has%20a%20presence%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730829660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fb1cf0v9g_amin-patel-shaina-nc_625x300_05_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthree-time-winner-amin-patel-shaina-nc-fight-for-mumbadevi-6952120%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumba%20Devi%20is%20the%20presiding%20deity%20of%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20country's%20financial%20capital%2C%20and%20the%20constituency%20named%20after%20her%20is%20set%20for%20an%20epic%20battle%20this%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthree-time-winner-amin-patel-shaina-nc-fight-for-mumbadevi-6952120%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Calls%20BJP%20Leader%20%26quot%3BBangladeshi%26quot%3B%2C%20Himanta%20Sarma's%20%26quot%3BItalian%26quot%3B%20Rebuttal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETargeting%20Congress%20for%20trying%20to%20project%20a%20BJP%20bypoll%20candidate%20in%20Assam%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BBangladeshi%26quot%3B%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Sarma%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20questions%20can%20also%20be%20raised%20on%20the%20nationality%20of%20the%20Opposition%20party's%20top%20leader%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%20asked%20why%20Bengali%20Hindus%20from%20Bangladesh%20who%20have%20long%20been%20residents%20of%20India%2C%20should%20face%20criticism%20for%20being%20a%20candidate%20in%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20in%20its%20campaigning%20for%20the%20Dholai%20constituency%20in%20Barak%20Valley%2C%20has%20cast%20doubts%20about%20the%20citizenship%20of%20BJP%20candidate%20Nihar%20Ranjan%20Das%2C%20claiming%20that%20it%20was%20a%20BJP%20leader%20who%20first%20raised%20the%20allegation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20(Congress)%20call%20Nihar%20Ranjan%20Bangladeshi%2C%20I%20will%20also%20call%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20Italian.%20If%20you%20think%20I%20am%20afraid%20of%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20or%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20let%20me%20tell%20you%20I%20am%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20said%20addressing%20a%20rally%20for%20Mr%20Das%20at%20Palonghat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonia%20Gandhi%20who%20was%20born%20in%20Italy%20came%20to%20India%20in%201968%20after%20her%20marriage%20to%20Rajiv%20Gandhi.%20She%20was%20granted%20Indian%20citizenship%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20maintained%20that%20Bengali%20Hindu%20residents%20of%20the%20present%20Barak%20Valley%20of%20Assam%20were%20dwellers%20of%20what%20is%20now%20Bangladesh%2C%20as%20it%20was%20the%20same%20country%20prior%20to%20Partition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20blamed%20the%20Congress%20for%20creating%20the%20problems%20for%20Bengali-Hindus%20of%20Barak%20Valley%2C%20who%20had%20to%20move%20to%20present-day%20Assam%20following%20Partition%20of%20the%20country%20due%20to%20atrocities%20on%20religious%20minorities%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20campaign%2C%20I%20had%20come%20here%20and%20said%20that%20we%20will%20resolve%20all%20problems%20of%20the%20Bengali%20Hindus.%20The%20government%20of%20India%20has%20already%20unblocked%20the%20Aadhar%20cards%20that%20were%20on%20hold.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20also%20issued%20orders%20that%20Bengali%20Hindus%20should%20not%20face%20any%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20all%20problems%20have%20started%20to%20vanish%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20saying%20Mr%20Das%20is%20a%20Bangladeshi%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNihar%20Ranjan%20and%20his%20family%20have%20all%20the%20documents%20to%20prove%20their%20Indian%20citizenship.%20However%2C%20Congress%20is%20trying%20to%20rake%20up%20the%20issue.%20They%20want%20to%20make%20the%20Hindu%20Bengalis%20in%20Barak%20valley%20suffer%20once%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Sarma%20while%20replying%20to%20the%20Congress'%20allegation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20party%20is%20not%20insulting%20Nihar%20Ranjan%20alone%2C%20but%20all%20Bengali%20Hindus%2C%20he%20underlined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%20also%20held%20the%20Congress%20responsible%20for%20the%20Partition%20of%20India%20in%201947.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHad%20you%20not%20bifurcated%20Bharat%2C%20atrocities%20on%20Hindus%20in%20Bangladesh%20would%20not%20have%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHindus%20are%20facing%20atrocities%20even%20now%20(in%20Bangladesh).%20We%20can%20see%20this%20on%20television%20and%20social%20media.%20But%20you%20(Congress)%20cannot%20raise%20these%20issues.%20Congress%20was%20formed%20to%20play%20only%20negative%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20swipe%20at%20Congress%20poll%20performance%2C%20Mr%20Sarma%20advised%20the%20party%20to%20sit%20at%20home%20and%20get%20some%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20should%20sit%20at%20home%20and%20take%20rest.%20They%20won't%20come%20to%20power%20for%20another%2050%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%2C%20who%20had%20been%20busy%20with%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Jharkhand%20as%20the%20BJP's%20co-in-charge%20there%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy-elections%20are%20scheduled%20in%20five%20Assembly%20constituencies%20of%20the%20state%20on%20November%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Dholai%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20candidates%20in%20Samaguri%20and%20Behali%20seats%2C%20while%20its%20allies%20AGP%20is%20contesting%20from%20Bongaigaon%20and%20UPPL%20from%20Sidli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20by-polls%20were%20necessitated%20by%20the%20election%20of%20the%20incumbent%20MLAs%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Of%20these%20five%20seats%2C%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20held%20four%2C%20with%20