ompanies%2Fnews%2Fihcl-acquires-55-stake-in-rajscape-hotels-to-enhance-experiential-leisure-124110501518_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rajscape%20Hotels%20manages%2016%20boutique%20properties%20under%20the%20brand%20'Tree%20of%20Life%20Resorts%20%26amp%3B%20Hotels'%20across%20India%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fihcl-acquires-55-stake-in-rajscape-hotels-to-enhance-experiential-leisure-124110501518_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhatever%20The%20Verdict...%26quot%3B%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%20On%20Kamala%20Harris%20vs%20Donald%20Trump%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20seen%20%26quot%3Bsteady%20progress%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20ties%20with%20America%20over%20the%20last%20five%20presidencies%2C%20and%20its%20%26quot%3Brelationship%20with%20the%20US%20will%20only%20grow%26quot%3B%20irrespective%20of%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20US%20election%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20query%20during%20a%20joint%20press%20briefing%20with%20his%20Australian%20counterpart%20Penny%20Wong%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20also%20expressed%20optimism%20about%20the%20future%20of%20the%20Quad%2C%20which%20comprises%20the%20US%2C%20India%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWong%20told%20reporters%20that%20Australia%20saw%20the%20four-nation%20grouping%20%26quot%3Bretaining%20its%20importance%20regardless%20of%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20election%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMillions%20of%20Americans%20headed%20towards%20polling%20stations%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20elect%20the%2047th%20President%20of%20the%20US%2C%20capping%20one%20of%20the%20most%20bitter%20presidential%20campaigns%20in%20the%20country's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20nominee%20and%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%2060%2C%20and%C2%A0%20Republican%20leader%20and%20former%20US%20president%20Donald%20Trump%2C%2078%2C%20remained%20neck%20and%20neck%20in%20polls%20conducted%20by%20various%20media%20outlets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20ministers%20were%20asked%20if%20there%20was%20a%20concern%20about%20Trump%20winning%20the%20election%20and%20if%20the%20Quad%20would%20be%20affected%20under%20his%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20actually%20seen%20steady%20progress%20in%20our%20relationship%20with%20the%20US%20over%20the%20last%20five%20presidencies%2C%20including%20an%20earlier%20Trump%20presidency.%20So%2C%20when%20we%20look%20at%20the%20American%20election%2C%20we%20are%20very%20confident%20that%20whatever%20the%20verdict%2C%20our%20relationship%20with%20the%20United%20States%20will%20only%20grow%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20terms%20of%20the%20Quad%2C%20I%20remind%20you%20that%20it%20was%20revived%20under%20a%20Trump%20presidency%20in%202017.%20It%20was%20then%20moved%20from%20the%20level%20of%20a%20permanent%20secretary%20to%20a%20minister%2C%20also%20during%20the%20Trump%20presidency%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20it's%20interesting%2C%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20Covid%2C%20when%20physical%20meetings%20had%20stopped%2C%20one%20of%20the%20rare%20physical%20meetings%20of%20Foreign%20Ministers%20was%20actually%20of%20the%20Quad%2C%20in%20Tokyo%2C%20in%202020.%20So%20I%20think%20that%20should%20tell%20us%20something%20about%20the%20prospect%20of%20the%20Quad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%2C%20Japan%2C%20India%2C%20and%20Australia%20had%20in%202017%20given%20shape%20to%20the%20long-pending%20proposal%20of%20setting%20up%20the%20%26quot%3BQuad%26quot%3B%20or%20the%20Quadrilateral%20coalition%20to%20counter%20China's%20aggressive%20behaviour%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four-member%20Quad%2C%20or%20the%20Quadrilateral%20Secu