aluru%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Akshata%20Murty%2C%20visited%20the%20Raghavendra%20Swamy%20Mutt%20in%20Bengaluru%20with%20his%20in-laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfosys%20co-founder%20Narayan%20Murthy%20and%20philanthropist%20Sudha%20Murthy%20accompanied%20their%20daughter%20and%20son-in-law%20at%20the%20mutt.%20The%20family%20joined%20the%20aarti.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Akshata%20Murty%20and%20her%20daughters%20Anoushka%20and%20Krishna%20visited%20the%20mutt%20with%20her%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20who%20became%20the%20first%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Hindu%20origin%2C%20has%20ancestral%20roots%20in%20India.%C2%A0Last%20year%2C%20he%20visited%20the%20Akshardham%20Temple%20in%20Delhi%20with%20his%20wife%20before%20attending%20the%20G20%20Summit.%20During%20their%20time%20at%20the%20temple%2C%20they%20performed%20puja%20and%20%3Cem%3Eabhishek%3C%2Fem%3E%20(the%20ritual%20pouring%20of%20water%20on%20the%20deity's%20idol)%20and%20interacted%20with%20the%20swamis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20Southampton%2C%20England%2C%20but%20his%20appointment%20as%20the%20first%20prime%20minister%20of%20colour%20has%20been%20cheered%20by%20Indians%20who%20see%20him%20as%20a%20son%20of%20the%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sunak%20has%20been%20vocal%20about%20his%20Indian%20roots%20and%20his%20religious%20beliefs.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20hugely%20proud%20of%20my%20Indian%20roots%20and%20my%20connections%20to%20India...being%20a%20proud%20Hindu%20means%20I%20will%20always%20have%20a%20connection%20to%20India%20and%20the%20people%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Sunak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Mr%20Sunak%20attended%20a%20Ram%20Katha%20at%20Cambridge%20University%20on%20India's%20Independence%20Day%2C%20he%20proclaimed%20that%20he%20was%20there%20%26quot%3Bnot%20as%20a%20Prime%20Minister%20but%20as%20a%20Hindu%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20he%20was%20elected%20as%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Conservative%20Party%2C%20becoming%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20replacing%20Liz%20Truss%20who%20had%20a%20short%2045-day%20stint%20in%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Conservatives%20were%20ousted%20by%20the%20Labour%20Party%20led%20by%20Keir%20Starmer%2C%20ending%20their%2014-year%20drought.%20The%20Conservatives%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Tories%2C%20won%20just%20121%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20Labour%20secured%20412%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Commons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730820660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fe0s0j44o_rishi-sunak_625x300_05_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-uk-ex-pm-rishi-sunak-wife-akshata-murty-offer-prayers-in-bengaluru-6951218%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Rishi%20Sunak%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Akshata%20Murty%20visited%20the%20Raghavendra%20Swamy%20Mutt%20in%20Bengaluru%20with%20his%20in-laws.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-uk-ex-pm-rishi-sunak-wife-akshata-murty-offer-prayers-in-bengaluru-6951218%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWill%20Demolish%20Artificial%20Barrier%20Of%2050%25%20Reservations%26quot%3B%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECaste%20discrimination%20in%20India%20is%20%26quot%3Bunique%26quot%3B%20--%20probably%20among%20worst%20in%20world%20--%20and%20the%20Congress%20will%20demolish%20the%20%26quot%3Bartificial%20barrier%26quot%3B%20of%2050%20per%20cent%20reservations%2C%20the%20party's%20senior%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20today.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20is%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-karnataka-telangana-gets-ready-for-caste-census-6944020%5C%22%3ETelangana%2C%20which%20is%20becoming%20the%20second%20Congress-ruled%20state%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20Karnataka%20to%20undertake%20a%20caste%20census.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caste%20survey%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20state%20government%20from%20November%206%20and%20it%20will%20continue%20till%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%2C%20along%20with%20party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20was%20attending%20a%20meeting%20organised%20by%20the%20state%20Congress%2C%20where%20he%20interacted%20with%20social%20groups%2C%20caste%20associations%20and%20state%20leaders%20and%20other%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20resolved%20to%20conduct%20caste%20survey%20along%20with%20economic%20mapping%20to%20reveal%20who%20are%20the%20India's%20poor%20and%20what%20percentage%20of%20population%20they%20comprise.%20This%2C%20the%20party%20maintains%2C%20will%20help%20to%20do%20away%20with%20the%2050%20per%20cent%20cap%20on%20reservations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Hindi%20post%20on%20X%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20said%20the%20steps%20would%20%26quot%3BX-Ray%26quot%3B%20the%20country%20and%20provide%20correct%20reservations%2C%20rights%20and%20share%20to%20everyone%2C%20Mr.%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20previous%20panel%20of%20backwards%20castes%20was%20based%20on%20a%201993%20law%20and%20had%20mandate%20only%20to%20gather%20data%20on%20education%20and%20employment%20quota.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20Telangana%20census%20will%20gather%20socioeconomic%20profile%20of%20all%20castes%2C%20sources%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E48%2C000%20teachers%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20deployed%20for%20the%20survey%2C%20for%20which%20primary%20schools%20will%20work%20only%20half-day%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20will%20go%20from%20house-to-house%20and%20conduct%20survey%20to%20collect%20data.%20This%20will%20encompass%20social%2C%20educatio