%20with%20these%20traditional%20versions%2C%20Tarana%20discovered%20some%20dishes%20that%20have%20stayed%20true%20to%20their%20roots.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EYarkhandi%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Epulao%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDocumenting%20changing%20food%20habits%20across%20geographies%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20at%20a%20nondescript%20food%20stall%20in%20Ladakh%20where%20JNU%20(Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20New%20Delhi)%20PhD%20scholar%2C%20Fida%20Husain%E2%80%99s%20aunt%20Ama%20Haji%20would%20get%20her%20fill%20of%20%3Cem%3EYarkhandi%20pulao%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20her%20essay%2C%20Fida%20writes%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3EYarkandi%20polla%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereflects%20the%20cultural%20heritage%20of%20Ladakh%20as%20a%20confluence%20of%20cultures.%20%E2%80%9CMade%20the%20traditional%20way%20%E2%80%94%20slow-cooked%20in%20a%20heavy%20stone%20pot%20called%20a%20%3Cem%3Edoltok%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20%3Cem%3ELadakhi%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20the%20dish%20was%20said%20to%20be%20symbolic%20of%20the%20big%20hearts%20(read%3A%20deep%20pockets)%20of%20the%20hosts%20for%20their%20guests.%20This%20bounty%20was%20proven%20by%20the%20amount%20of%20fat%2Fghee%20dripping%20down%20one%E2%80%99s%20elbows%20while%20eating.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFun%20fact%3A%20Ladakh%20was%20a%20stranger%20to%20rice%2C%20the%20protagonist%20of%20the%20dish%2C%20until%20about%20seven%20decades%20ago.%20It%20was%20improved%20transport%20links%20and%20connectivity%20that%20transformed%20the%20once%20luxury%20item%20into%20a%20staple%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282445%2Findia-in-pics-ten-local-ladakhi-dish-history-cult