elf-styled%20political%20pundits%20including%20yours%20truly%20should%20consider%20this%20election%20a%20refresher%20course.%20This%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20complex%20elections%20India%20has%20seen%2C%20where%20conventional%20wisdom%20and%20existing%20political%20theories%20may%20count%20for%20nothing%20once%20the%20people's%20verdict%20is%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contest%20is%20so%20fragmented%20that%20legacy%20data%20is%20of%20little%20use%20to%20strategists%20hoping%20to%20read%20the%20voters'%20minds.%20Not%20only%20has%20the%20number%20of%20parties%20increased%20exponentially%2C%20but%20the%20average%20number%20of%20candidates%20per%20constituency%20has%20surged%20as%20well%E2%80%94from%20nine%20in%202004%20to%2011%20in%202019%2C%20and%20now%2014.%20That%20too%20after%20a%20record%20withdrawal%20of%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EComplex%20Regional%20Dynamics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImagine%20an%20average%20of%2014%20candidates%E2%80%94some%20rebels%2C%20some%20propped%20up%20as%20independents%20and%20many%20official%20party%20candidates%E2%80%94in%20each%20of%20Maharashtra's%20288%20constituencies.%20Add%20in%20factors%20like%20caste%2C%20region%2C%20religion%2C%20and%20urban-rural%20dynamics%2C%20and%20the%20picture%20is%20anything%20but%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20not%20all.%20In%20traditional%20Shiv%20Sena%20strongholds%20like%20Konkan%20and%20Mumbai%2C%20it%20is%20Sena%20versus%20Sena%20competing%20for%20dominance.%20In%20regions%20with%20a%20significant%20Maratha%20presence%E2%80%94North%2C%20Marathwada%2C%20and%20West%E2%80%94it%20is%20going%20to%20be%20NCP%20(Nationalist%20Congress%20Party)%20versus%20NCP.%20As%20per%20the%20latest%20count%2C%20two%20rival%20Sena%20factions%E2%80%94one%20led%20by%20the%20current%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20other%20by%20his%20predecessor%E2%80%94will%20face%20off%20in%2049%20assembly%20seats.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20two%20NCP%20factions%20will%20compete%20in%2038%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20guesses%20as%20to%20which%20way%20the%20Marathas%20will%20vote%20or%20how%20the%20Hindutva%20factor%20will%20play%20out%20in%20these%20Sena%20and%20NCP%20clashes%3F%20In%20Vidarbha%2C%20a%20relatively%20underdeveloped%20region%2C%20the%20classical%20battle%20between%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20the%20Congress%20continues%2C%20with%20loyalties%20shifting%20frequently.%20Which%20way%20will%20it%20go%20this%20time%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVidarbha%20is%20known%20for%20its%20closely%20contested%20elections%2C%20though%20there%20have%20been%20some%20exceptions.%20In%20the%202014%20assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20dominated%2C%20winning%2044%20out%20of%20the%2062%20seats%20available%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20managed%20only%2010.%20By%20the%20next%20election%2C%20the%20BJP's%20tally%20fell%20to%2029%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20Congress's%20improved%20to%2015.%20However%2C%20in%20this%20year's%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20there%20was%20a%20significant%20shift%3A%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20led%20in%2042%20assembly%20segments%2C%20reducing%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20to%20just%2019.%20Will%20the%20region%20flip%20again%20as%20it%20has%20done%20all%20too%20frequently%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20about%20regional%20shifts%20either%E2%80%94there%20are%20complexities%20within%20complexities.%20Consider%20these%20examples%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20remains%20unclear%20how%20Maratha%20quota%20leader%20Manoj%20Jarange%20Patil's%20decision%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20electoral%20race%20will%20play%20out.%20Both%20the%20NDA%20and%20MVA%20claim%20the%20move%20will%20benefit%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhich%20alliance%20will%20be%20more%20affected%20by%20the%2025%20candidates%20from%20Raj%20Thackeray's%20Maharashtra%20Navnirman%20Sena%20(MNS)%20%C2%A0in%20the%20Mumbai%20region%E2%80%94the%20NDA%20or%20the%20MVA%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDespite%20numerous%20efforts%20by%20top%20leaders%20from%20both%20major%20alliances%2C%2018%20NDA%20rebels%20and%2022%20MVA%20rebels%20remain%20in%20the%20race.%20Will%20voters%20adhere%20to%20the%20official%20party%20line%20and%20reject%20the%20rebel%20candidates%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20some%20constituencies%2C%20while%20the%20official%20party%20candidate%20has%20withdrawn%2C%20the%20rebels%20remain%20in%20the%20race.%20How%20will%20this%20impact%20the%20election%20results%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20will%20happen%20in%20constituencies%20like%20Mumbai's%20Mahim%2C%20where%20the%20NDA%20has%20chosen%20to%20support%20Raj%20Thackeray's%20son%2C%20while%20the%20sitting%20MLA%20from%20the%20ruling%20party%20refuses%20to%20back%20down%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20it's%20up%20to%20you%20to%20analyse%20the%20numbers%2C%20calculate%20the%20potential%20impacts%2C%20and%20draw%20your%20conclusions%E2%80%94putting%20your%20math%20skills%20to%20the%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERegion-Wise%20Voting%20Patterns%20In%202019%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Statutory%20Warning%3A%20Drawing%20conclusions%20based%20on%20past%20elections%20can%20be%20risky!%20Alliance%20have%20changed%20widely%20between%202019%20and%202024%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Statutory%20Warning%3A%20Drawing%20conclusions%20based%20on%20past%20elections%20can%20be%20risky!%20Alliance%20have%20changed%20widely%20between%202019%20and%202024%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F8iksashg_maharashtra_625x300_05_November_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStatutory%20Warning%3A%20Drawing%20conclusions%20based%20on%20past%20elections%20can%20be%20risky!%20Alliances%20have%20changed%20drastically%20between%202019%20and%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMushrooming%20Political%20Entrepreneurship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20interested%20in%20political%20entrepreneurship%2C%20Maharashtra%20is%20the%20place%20to%20watch.%20Rarely%20has%20an%20election%20seen%20so%20many%20contestants%E2%80%94independents%2C%20smaller%20parties%2C%20and%20two%20alliances%20with%20six%20parties%20each.%20Established%20players%20dominate%20the%20field%2C%20but%20tensions%20within%20alliances%20have%20led%20to%20a%20surge%20of%20rebels%20and%20independents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20aspirants%20hope%20that%20the%20threshold%20for%20winning%20will%20be%20lower%20this%20time%2C%20increasing%20their%20chances.%20Though%20the%20major%20alliances%20may%20not%20admit%20this%2C%20some%20leaders%20in%20both%20the%20MVA%20and%20the%20NDA%20have%20strategically%20fielded%20vote-cutters%20and%20rebels%20to%20spoil%20their%20opponents'%20chances.%20The%20sheer%20number%20of%20independents%20reflects%20a%20belief%20that%20Maharashtra%20may%20have%20a%20lower%20entry%20barrier.%20Some%20of%20these%20political%20startups%20could%20gain%20a%20premium%20post-verdict%2C%20while%20others%20may%20just%20fade%20away%2C%20only%20to%20resurrect%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Masterclass%20In%20Election%20Management%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20election%20is%20also%20a%20masterclass%20in%20managing%20a%20campaign%20down%20to%20the%20last%20voter.%20All%20six%20major%20players%20are%20seasoned%2C%20yet%20the%20contest%20tests%20their%20mettle%20as%20the%20voter%20remains%20tight-lipped%2C%20keeping%20everyone%20guessing.%20Will%20voters%20keep%20each%20party%20on%20tenterhooks%2C%20or%20will%20they%20deliver%20a%20decisive%20verdict%20in%20favour%20of%20an%20alliance%3F%20No%20one%20knows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%2C%20however%2C%20is%20visible%20to%20discerning%20eyes%3A%20a%20thoughtful%2C%20silent%20voter.%20The%20messaging%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20backed%20by%20local%20%3Cem%3Eyatras%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20rally%20caste%20groups%2C%20is%20meant%20to%20complement%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20focus%20on%20the%20Ladki%20Behna%20scheme%2C%20with%20four%20to%20five%20instalments%20already%20delivered.%20There's%20also%20a%20stark%20contrast%20between%20the%20understated%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20the%20more%20vocal%20Congress%2C%20ever%20eager%20for%20the%20limelight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20election%20has%20truly%20become%20a%20seat-by-seat%20battle.%20Broad%20state-wide%20or%20even%20regional%20trends%20won't%20capture%20the%20intricacies.%20Each%20seat%20will%20tell%20its%20own%20story.%20And%20that%20is%20fascinating%20for%20the%20complexities%20involved%2C%20as%20listed%20above%20in%20detail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20bustle%20of%20electioneering%2C%20many%20factors%20will%20likely%20influence%20voters%E2%80%94some%20confusing%2C%20some%20promising%2C%20and%20some%20simply%20inexplicable.%20Maharashtra%20continues%20to%20attract%20the%20lion's%20share%20of%20foreign%20direct%20investment%20(FDI)%2C%20totalling%2052.4%25%20of%20the%20country's%20FDI%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20the%20current%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20also%20has%20a%20robust%20pipeline%20of%20projects%20generating%20thousands%20of%20quality%20jobs.%20It%20hosts%20India's%20auto%20hub%2C%20financial%20hub%2C%20entertainment%20hub%2C%20and%20a%20thriving%20startup%20ecosystem%2C%20which%20is%20second%20to%20none.%20Despite%20so%20much%20going%20right%2C%20Marathas%E2%80%94one%20of%20the%20dominant%20social%20groups%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%94are%20demanding%20quota%20for%20themselves.%20Why%20is%20that%3F%20Is%20a%20fractured%20polity%20with%20a%20surge%20of%20candidates%20and%20parties%20to%20voters'%20liking%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWise%20voters%20will%20weigh%20all%20these%20factors%E2%80%94and%20more%E2%80%94while%20casting%20their%20votes.%20The%20guessing%20game%20will%20continue.%20After%20all%2C%20we%20are%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20one%20of%20India's%20most%20complex%20and%20unpredictable%20elections%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3