problem-solving%20solutions.%20The%20encouraging%20results%20from%20our%20test%20beds%20give%20us%20confidence%20in%20expanding%20these%20practices%20across%20the%20farmlands%20in%20order%20to%20address%20critical%20air%20quality%20issues%20from%20stubble%20burning.%20This%20initiative%20aligns%20with%20Merino%E2%80%99s%20mission%20of%20promoting%20Universal%20Weal%20through%20trade%20and%20industry%2C%20contributing%20to%20both%20environmental%20and%20societal%20well-being%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mr%20Lohia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcpcb.nic.in%2Fuploads%2FAQM%2FTERI_Brief_Report.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDoes%20air%20quality%20from%20crop%20residue%20burning%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20residential%20areas%20adversely%20affect%20respiratory%20health%3F%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%2C%20Published%20in%20October%202021.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ceew.in%2Fblogs%2Fpunjab-farmers-explain-why-they-burn-crop-stubble%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGround%20Zero%3A%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20Farmers%20Explain%20Why%20They%20Burn%20Stubble%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Srish%20Prakash%20and%20L.%20S.%20Kurinji%2C%20Published%20on%2015%20November%202021.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-54930380%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStubble%20burning%3A%20Why%20it%20continues%20to%20smother%20north%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20BBC%2C%20Published%20