9CIf%20a%20boy%20sees%20his%20favourite%20celebrity%20being%20open%20and%20vulnerable%2C%20he%20will%20realise%20that%20he%20too%20can%20share%20his%20feelings.%20Modern%20masculinity%20is%20about%20embracing%20yourselves%20and%20accepting%20who%20you%20are%2C%20rather%20than%20conforming%20to%20what%20the%20world%20expects%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20stresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20show%20has%20been%20a%20hit%2C%20igniting%20important%20conversations%20around%20men%E2%80%99s%20mental%20health%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20masculinity.%20As%20Javed%20Akhtar%20poignantly%20stated%20on%20the%20show%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20angry%20young%20man%20is%20not%20just%20angry%2C%20he%20is%20deeply%20hurt.%20%3Cem%3EMard%20ko%20dard%20kyun%20nahi%20hota%3F%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5BWhy%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20a%20man%20feel%20hurt%3F%5D%20Is%20there%20some%20problem%3F%20%3Cem%3EHona%20chahiye%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BHe%20should%20feel%5D.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20hopes%20that%20through%20the%20show%2C%20we%20learn%20to%20embrace%20and%20accept%20ourselves.%20He%20has%20a%20message%20for%20every%20young%20person%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20they%20identify%20as%20male%2C%20female%2C%20or%20queer%3A%20%E2%80%9CMake%20money%2C%20but%20also%20make%20time%20for%20yourself.%20Be%20kind%20to%20yourself.%20All%20that%20matters%20is%20a%20good%20family%20and%20friend%20circle%2C%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20great%20memories.%20Maximise%20your%20time%20with%20your%20loved%20ones.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20my%20favourite%20episodes%20from%20the%20series%20%3Cem%3EBe%20A%20Man%2C%20Yaar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20actor%20Imran%20Khan%20candidly%20shared%20his%20struggles%20with%20mental%20health.%20Discussing%20the%20stigma%20around%20therapy%2C%20he%20remarked%20how%20it%E2%80%99s%20often%20looked%20down%20upon%20to%20%E2%80%9Clie%20down%20on%20a%20couch%20and%20talk%20about%20feelings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20do%20you%20respect%20a%20man%20who%20is%20not%20earning%3F%20How%20d