manhood%E2%80%99%20after%20a%20vasectomy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20through%20extensive%20education%20that%20dispels%20these%20misconceptions%2C%20the%20doctors%20are%20starting%20to%20see%20a%20shift%20in%20attitudes.%20The%20statistics%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Andheri%20centre%20has%20completed%2055%2C000%20family%20planning%20surgeries%20%E2%80%94%20are%20a%20nod%20to%20these%20mindset%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EQuality%20healthcare%20at%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20doorstep%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20state-of-the-art%20services%20and%20consultations%20are%20made%20available%20to%20the%20patients%20who%20head%20to%20the%20L%26amp%3BT%20centres%2C%20there%20was%20a%20burgeoning%20need%20to%20extend%20the%20same%20to%20those%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20this%20privilege.%20This%20gap%20is%20bridged%20by%20the%20Mobile%20Health%20Units%2C%20which%20take%20medical%20services%20to%20the%20urban%2C%20peri-urban%2C%20as%20well%20as%20far-flung%20rural%20and%20tribal%20poor%2C%20explains%20Dahlia%20Sengupta%2C%20a%20volunteer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2015%20years%20Sengupta%20has%20co-ordinated%20this%20enormous%20exercise%20that%20provides%20services%20to%20beneficiaries%20from%20rural%20communities%20within%20a%20short%20radius%20of%20where%20they%20live.%20Through%20weekly%2C%20monthly%20and%20need-based%20interventions%2C%20these%20mobile%20health%20units%20reach%20out%20to%20slum%20areas%20spread%20across%20Mumbai%20city%2C%20Navi%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Thane.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20%5Bslum%20dwellers%5D%20do%20not%20have%20the%20time%20to%20take%20a%20break%20from%20their%20work%20and%20head%20to%20the%20health%20centres%20for%20a%20check-up%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sengupta%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201720px)%20100vw%2C%201720px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fimg