20but%20also%20benefit%20from%20conservation%20activities.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20penny%20goes%20to%20the%20tribal%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20Women%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20have%20become%20leaders%20in%20the%20fight%20against%20poaching.%20Whether%20it%20be%20exercising%20their%20right%20of%20civic%20arrest%20or%20taking%20to%20the%20streets%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20mining%20lobby%2C%20Padmaja%20describes%20how%20women%20rally%20together%20to%20protect%20their%20environment%2C%20offsetting%20the%20traditional%20gender%20dynamics%20in%20rural%20Rajasthan.%20By%20employing%20these%20women%20in%20the%20camp%2C%20teaching%20them%20self%20defence%2C%20and%20educating%20them%2C%20Bhagheera%E2%80%99s%20camp%20serves%20as%20a%20means%20of%20confidence%20building%20and%20economic%20empowerment.%20It%20provides%20women%20with%20the%20tools%20and%20knowledge%20to%20take%20on%20leadership%20roles%20in%20conservation%20and%20fosters%20a%20sense%20of%20agency%20that%20benefits%20both%20wildlife%20and%20the%20broader%20community.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20Bagheera%E2%80%99s%20Camp%20is%20not%20one%20of%20instant%20gratification%3B%20it%20is%20about%20slow%20and%20steady%20work%2C%20akin%20to%20the%20patient%20nurturing%20of%20a%20young%20sapling.%20Padmaja%E2%80%99s%20dream%20is%20a%20contagious%20one.%20It%20is%20a%20call%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20whispers%20of%20the%20wind%20through%20the%20trees%2C%20to%20feel%20the%20cool%20earth%20beneath%20our%20feet.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20call%20to%20remember%20that%20we%20are%20not%20separate%20from%20nature%2C%20but%20integral%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Padmaja%20herself%20says%2C%20citing%20the%20wisdom%20of%20her%20ancestors%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20greatly%20inspired%20by%20the%20water%20conservation%20systems%20of%20Marwar%2C%20of%20Mehrangarh%20Fort%20(Jodhpur).%20Our%20ancestors%20managed%20to%20carve%20out%20a%20water%20catchment%20in%20a%20place%20called%20%E2%80%98Marudhar%2C%E2%80%9